{
  "stem": "7684.9",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told me what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told me, that I had-- in Polish-- that I had to push.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I pushed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the baby didn't came out, because it was the six month laying flat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was three months later, not that it happened-- laying flat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so, you know, they-- And then the German doctors didn't want to touch me when I had that sickness, that scabies.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they say to me, if you don't stop screaming, we'll throw you out of the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, one of the women, in Polish, say, the head is already out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then when somebody came, and brought me on the table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the baby was born.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I had to walk to the table, back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] then I was laying there [INAUDIBLE] nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chaim still didn't know there was a baby born.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So after three days, I think, he found out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the doctors didn't want to touch me, because I had that very, very contagious skin disease.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they looked all the time under the bed if I was breathing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then there would be something wrong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, after five days and five nights, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Chaim came and picked me up with a horse and carriage, and brought me to that apartment there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I didn't know what to do with a baby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made a clothes for my-- Chaim bought already some underpants and things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he bought once a dress.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I made my own clothes for this baby, by hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I sewed it by hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had no idea what clothes baby-- but I had clothes for the baby.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
